						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/Commodities/Fisheries/Related-developments/New-large-scale-aquaponics-project-funded-by-the-EU-aiming-at-optimized-food-and-water-management" title="New large-scale aquaponics project funded by the EU, aiming at optimized food and water management  " alt="link">New large-scale aquaponics project funded by the EU, aiming at optimized food and water management  </a></h2>

	
					<p>The newly started collaborative project INAPRO (innovative model and demonstration based water management for resource efficiency in integrated multi-trophic agriculture and aquaculture systems) aims at achieving a real breakthrough towards implementation and commercialization of aquaponics systems. INAPRO’s project coordination is located at the Leibniz Institute of Freshwater Ecology and Inland Fisheries (IGB) in Berlin, Germany. INAPRO will build on the technological basis of an earlier project by IGB that developed a very efficient tomato-and-fish aquaponics system. Prototypes will be tested in Europe and China. &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://www.alphagalileo.org/ViewItem.aspx?ItemId=138845&amp;CultureCode=en" target="_self">http://www.alphagalileo.org/ViewItem.aspx?ItemId=138845&amp;CultureCode=en</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;(AlphaGalileo, 10/02/2014) &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
							<p><span class="date">28/02/2014</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/Commodities/Fisheries/Related-developments/New-large-scale-aquaponics-project-funded-by-the-EU-aiming-at-optimized-food-and-water-management">Read more...</a>
</div>
