						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/Commodities/Fisheries/Related-developments/Caribbean-fisheries-specific-FAO-FIRMS-factsheet-for-the-Western-Central-Atlantic-Region" title="Caribbean fisheries: specific FAO FIRMS factsheet for the Western Central Atlantic Region" alt="link">Caribbean fisheries: specific FAO FIRMS factsheet for the Western Central Atlantic Region</a></h2>

	
					<p>The FAO has released an updated version of its factsheet for the Western Central Atlantic Region (that includes the Caribbean region). It is available on the FAO’s Fishery Resources Monitoring System (FIRMS) website. The factsheet is a comprehensive assessment and dataset on the region’s fisheries, and includes information on catches, stock management, and the biological state and trends of stock. &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://firms.fao.org/firms/resource/11842/en" target="_self">http://firms.fao.org/firms/resource/11842/en</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;(FAO, 2013)</p>
