						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/Commodities/Fisheries/Related-developments/Sustainable-aquaculture-and-plant-based-fish-feed" title="Sustainable aquaculture and plant-based fish feed" alt="link">Sustainable aquaculture and plant-based fish feed</a></h2>

	
					<p>Researchers at the at the Institute of Marine and Environmental Technology (University of Maryland, USA) have developed a plant-based fish food adapted to marine fish species One new ingredient that proved to be key in the diet consumption was taurine.<a href="http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2012-08-19/features/bs-gr-vegetarian-fish-meal-20120819_1_fish-oil-aquaculture-striped-bass" target="_self">http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2012-08-19/features/bs-gr-vegetarian-fish-meal-20120819_1_fish-oil-aquaculture-striped-bass</a>Similar research on plant-based fish feed was conducted in Norway:<a href="http://phys.org/news/2012-11-fish-sustainable-aquaculture.html" target="_self">http://phys.org/news/2012-11-fish-sustainable-aquaculture.html</a></p>
							<p><span class="date">22/05/2013</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
