						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/Commodities/Fisheries/Related-developments/Supporting-lobster-protection-in-Bahamas" title="Supporting lobster protection in Bahamas" alt="link">Supporting lobster protection in Bahamas</a></h2>

	
					<p>The Global Environment Facility (GEF) Small Grants Programme (SGP) is funding a project on the Bahamas island Abaco, to conserve the lobster population by training fishermen in sustainable fishing practices”. These include: sustainable catch practices that do not catch juvenile lobsters, and use of gauges to measure the acceptable catch size. The project conducted community education efforts aimed at encouraging the public not to buy undersized lobsters. Spot checks revealed full compliance by the fishermen.<a href="http://goo.gl/RqOac" target="_self">http://goo.gl/RqOac</a>(GEF SPC, 10/12/2013)</p>
							<p><span class="date">22/05/2013</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/Commodities/Fisheries/Related-developments/Supporting-lobster-protection-in-Bahamas">Read more...</a>
